FT  07 DEC 94 / UK Company News: Marley US deal
General Shale Products, the US subsidiary of Marley, has acquired two
concrete block manufacturing plants from Bristol Steel for Dollars 3.8m
(Pounds 2.31m) in cash.
The acquisitions, Bristol Concrete Products Corpn and Tri-State Concrete
Company, are situated in Bristol, Virginia, and Kingsport, Tennessee, close
to two of General Shale's existing concrete block operations.
